title: Ep. 819 - Is The Plan Still On? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Everyone is excited for Holi and as usual Iyer is skeptic of Jetha's plan and asks him to be sure whether tomorrow's Holi plan will be implemented or not. Jetha tells him to be rest assured that it's on!

title: Ep. 820 - Bagha Is In A Dilemma - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: A senior inspector is divisioned near Jethalal's office as they're suspecting 2 criminals in that area. Meanwhile, 2 of Bagha's friend are in urgent need of shelter as they claim that the police is behind them. What will Bagha do?

title: Ep. 821 - Baga Keeps A Secret - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga helps his friends and asks them to hide in a carton. They try to escape but eventually return to the godown. Baga is tensed as they ask him to help them stay there for a night. He is scared to know that shop will remain close the next day.

title: Ep. 822 - Baga Takes A Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga is worried as he is unable to decide on what should be done. He decides to inform Jethalal about this but later, he sneakily takes godown keys to help his friends flee.

title: Ep. 823 - The Holi Celebration - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham gathers at farmhouse to celebrate Holi. Natu kaka and Baga inform Jetha about Baga's friends hiding in the godown. Jetha looks up to Mehta for help.

title: Ep. 824 - Jetha, Baga And Nattu Kaka Under Arrest - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Police enquires of Jetha, Baga and Nattu kaka. Jetha tries to prove his innocence. Police put them behind bars. Finally, Baga's friends come to their rescue

title: Ep. 825 - Baga And Natu Kaka Are Sorry - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Baga and Natu Kaka bring a card for Jethalal asking for forgiveness. Taarak is assigned with work and Anjali decides to help him. Tapu Sena come to Mehta for help. Taarak is irritated.

title: Ep. 826 - Mehta And Dr. Haathi With Same Problem - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Taarak has a bad tooth ache after eating the beetle leaves offered by Jetha. He runs to Dr. Hathi to find out that he has the same problem. Jethalal sticks a tape on Daya's mouth to prevent her from talking.

title: Ep. 827 - Bhide Calls Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide asks everyone to gather at Jetha's house. Everyone creates a havoc as they have no reason to gather. The society's renovation has been stopped and now everyone is worried. Sunderlal is nowhere to be found to discuss this matter.

title: Ep. 828 - Sunderlal Shocks Everyone - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sunderlal tells everyone that he would need extra money to continue the renovation. Gokuldham society asks him the reason behind it and refuse to pay the extra money. Thus, he leaves.

title: Ep. 829 - Sunderlal Is Still The Same - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sunderlal gets mangoes for Jetha, in return asks for taxi fare. Daya decides to eat light food until Sunderlal is under stress. Following which Tapu and Champaklal decide to eat  the same food as Daya.

title: Ep. 830 - Daya On A Mission - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya thinks nobody trusts Sunderlal for which she has to talk to Jethalal. Daya gives an example of a customer as how Sunderlal should be treated. She asks Jetha to pay the extra money. Sunderlal convinces Daya as how he needs the money only for the

title: Ep. 831 - The Scheme - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sunder takes help from Baga to convince Jethalal to get the extra money. However, Jethalal, under a scheme, gives the money to Baga. Tapu Sena ask for celebration.

title: Ep. 832 - Sodhi Comes Drunk - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham holds a meeting to discuss on the celebration once the society renovation is done. Sodhi comes drunk to the meeting. Everyone asks him to calm down and to go home and take rest.

title: Ep. 833 - Worried Gokuldham - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide worries about the amount of money he will have to spend in the society opening ceremony. Jethalal worries about the society contract assigned to Sunderlal. Popatlal worries of which celebrity to call as guest in the opening ceremony.
